    <!-- Unity Section -->
    <div id="unity" class="section">
        <h3>Unity</h3>
        <p>Unity is a cross-platform game engine widely used for creating both 2D and 3D games. It has a large community and a wealth of resources for developers of all skill levels.</p>
        <a href="https://unity.com/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Unreal Engine Section -->
    <div id="unreal" class="section">
        <h3>Unreal Engine</h3>
        <p>Unreal Engine is a powerful real-time 3D creation tool used for games, architecture, films, and more. It is known for its high-quality visuals and robust toolset.</p>
        <a href="https://unrealengine.com/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Mentorship Programs Section -->
    <div id="mentorship" class="section">
        <h3>Mentorship Programs</h3>
        <p>The International Game Developers Association (IGDA) offers various mentorship programs connecting you with industry veterans who can provide guidance and advice.</p>
        <a href="https://igda.org/mentorship-programs" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Resources can be added below -->
</div>
